        <h1>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs) </h1>
  
        <div class="faq">
          <button class="accordion">
            1. How does this telemedicine platform help patients in remote areas?
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="pannel">
            <p>
              Telemedicine allows you to consult with healthcare providers remotely via video calls, phone calls, or chat, eliminating the need for in-person visits.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
  
        <div class="faq">
          <button class="accordion">
            2. How does it work?
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="pannel">
            <p>
                Our platform connects patients with certified doctors through video calls, chat, or virtual consultations, eliminating the need for long-distance travel. We also support multiple languages to make healthcare more accessible.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
  
        <div class="faq">
          <button class="accordion">
            3. Can I schedule an appointment at any time?
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="pannel">
            <p>
                Yes, you can book an appointment 24/7 based on doctor availability. Our platform ensures you get timely medical assistance.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
  
        <div class="faq">
          <button class="accordion">
            4. What kind of medical conditions can be treated via telemedicine?
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="pannel">
            <p>
                You can consult doctors for common illnesses like fever, infections, allergies, mental health concerns, chronic disease management, and more. However, emergencies require immediate in-person medical attention.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
  
        <div class="faq">
          <button class="accordion">
           5. Can I get an electronic prescription?
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="pannel">
            <p>
                Yes, after your consultation, the doctor can issue an electronic prescription, which you can download or have sent directly to a pharmacy.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
  
        <div class="faq">
          <button class="accordion">
            6. Is my personal and medical data secure?
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="pannel">
            <p>
                Absolutely. We use end-to-end encryption and comply with healthcare data protection regulations to ensure your privacy and security.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
